IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User root@lr0.org
PassCmd ~/configs/~s/getmupassword.sh
TLSType IMAPS
Port 993
AuthMechs LOGIN
#CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/mailbox/icloud/ 
Inbox ~/mailbox/icloud*Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *
